node.text:
Another day, another kitchen adventure. We made boba from scratch. Texture was just right, QQ the whole way through.
.
Kitchen is a sticky mess though. Tapioca flour + boiling water = glue, basically.😅
.
Small things we have time to appreciate these days. #familybonding #ramadan2020 Day 4 #circuitbreakersg Day 21
.
#keepcalm & make #boba
